# ✅ To-Do Web App

Developed as part of my internship with **SkillCraft Technology** 🌟

A responsive and user-friendly To-Do Web App that allows users to:
- ➕ Add and maintain tasks
- 📝 Edit or delete tasks
- ✅ Mark tasks as completed
- ⏰ Set Date and Time for each task
- 🗂️ Organize tasks in a clean list layout

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
